43.task: Touch exactly one object that is [partially but not all] blue.

TEACHER.observations: This was pretty fun. I think that teachers were able to communicate with their partners with the fact that they could call them back into the teaching area at any time; calling them back meant 'no' to whatever they were doing right before. I'm not completely sure whether the fact that this was an option was on purpose, but I found it really useful. If you prefer that people can't communicate in this way, you could make it so that after each map the teacher can decide whether to continue or bring the student back.
